    "description": "<strong>Gun Ugly</strong> is a surreal comedy action game from another dimension. It arrived by accident to take you on a journey you weren't expecting.<br><br>Rise through the ranks of Tactical Chaos Operations, uncover the conspiracy to fracture the multiverse, and save ALL the worlds.<br><br>With gunplay inspired by classic FPS games and a story inspired by the ramblings of a madman, Gun Ugly <strong><i>is</i></strong> Gun Ugly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879970/extras/46abc605b29765b96de6dded7561158a.poster.avif?t=1695305532\" width=460 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879970/extras/46abc605b29765b96de6dded7561158a.webm?t=1695305532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879970/extras/46abc605b29765b96de6dded7561158a.mp4?t=1695305532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A bizarre arsenal of overpowered weapons that you <i>will</i> use<br></li><li>Twenty dimension spanning levels - <i>&quot;Twenty's plenty!&quot;</i><br></li><li>A plot that in equal parts entertains, inspires, and brings into question our sanity<br></li><li>Over 15 entirely unique enemy types - <i>&quot;Wow, that's 16 enemies&quot;</i><br></li><li>High speed movement mechanics that will make real life feel boring<br></li><li>Absurdism<br></li><li>Functional graphics that enable the game to be played!<br></li><li>Adorable pupples</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879970/extras/e610772edea6d9d2e768953b69f832b9.avif?t=1695305532\" width=512 height=276 /></span>",
